The paper deals with a model of discrete dynamical system and its application in designing an adder circuit for multiple numbers in binary number system. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of computer science related to discrete structures (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), computational complexity (cs.CC), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), and scientific computing (cs.SC).
